    # game/areas/foggylake2foggy.rpy:775
    old "You lead her outside and reveal the head attached to your saddle. {color=#f6d6bd}Foggy’s{/color} eyes are wide open, and her grin turns into laughter. She grabs the head and moves it closer to her scarred face, looking deeply into its dead eyes. Next to her, the monster would be tiny. \n\n“You brought me a treat, love!” Her voice is so loud that {color=#f6d6bd}[horsename]{/color}, already disturbed by the smell of blood, steps away. “It’ll look plenty fine on my wall. {color=#f6d6bd}[foggy_shop_furlesswolftrophy_price] dragons{/color}!” She looks at you with a smile. “No soul in the North will give you more, and it will soon turn into a stinking pulp.” "
