    old "“You brought this here from {color=#f6d6bd}Howler’s{/color}?” She runs her fingers over the unpacked stack of fabric, then grins. “I want it!” She announces. “I won’t get something like this in {color=#f6d6bd}Creeks{/color}, and I could use a proper dress. I’ll give you {color=#f6d6bd}[foggy_shop_linen_price] dragons{/color} for it, take them, or I’m going to buy me another sack from {color=#f6d6bd}Akakios{/color}.” "
