    # game/areas/foggylake2foggy.rpy:1049
    old "“Oh dear!” She covers the egg with her massive hand, but sighs after noticing the unusual lightness. “Won’t even press a cloth on a table. I could, let me think, make a stand for it, a piece of wood here and here...” She illustrates how it would work with her fingers, then looks back at you only after you clear your throat. “I like it {color=#f6d6bd}[foggy_shop_griffonegg_price] dragons{/color} strong, love.” "
