    # game/areas/foggylake2foggy.rpy:2715
    old "“There are more of them than you can count, dear, most of them too small for a tree to take root. Strange tribes live on the larger ones, in the east and west. Here, the rocks stop any ships, boats, even. {color=#f6d6bd}High Island{/color} may be big and rich, but its volcano is too much of a threat for any settlers.” "
