    # game/areas/foggylake2foggy.rpy:2976
    old "“You must have crossed the mountain pass leading through {color=#f6d6bd}Hag Hills{/color}, aye? The old dolmen is in the east, {color=#f6d6bd}Pelt of the North{/color} and the ruins of {color=#f6d6bd}Steep House{/color} in the west. From there, it’s a long road to {color=#f6d6bd}Howler’s Dell{/color}.” "
