    # game/areas/foggylake2foggy.rpy:3671
    old "“That’s the furthest spot to the south where the foragers of {color=#f6d6bd}Creeks{/color} go. Such’n open area offers li’l to no hideouts, so larger beasts avoid it. Now that there isn’t much food for humans left, {color=#f6d6bd}Ilan{/color} and {color=#f6d6bd}Tzvi{/color} stay closer to the tavern.” "
