    # game/areas/foggylake2foggy.rpy:3714
    old "“I saw it myself, two decades ago. Crude like a dolmen, aye? We were seeking help from {color=#f6d6bd}The Tribe of The Green Mountain{/color}, and I’ve seen a druid from {color=#f6d6bd}Howler’s{/color} kneeling in front of the statue, for minutes. Like we would do to the empress, back in the capitol. But I saw no spells, it’s just a big piece of ugly rock.” "
